1.Long ago, Prometheus, the son of Lapetus, was the first man fashioned out of mud.
2. At the same time, Vulcan was making a woman out of mud.
3. Minerva sent the woman’s soul as a gift to the Gods
4. She was given the name “Pandora”
5. Pandora was given in marriage to Epitheo
6. Their first son was Pyrrha, the first mortal
